summary: Defines the foundational APIs of the Java SE Platform.
detail:
Defines the foundational APIs of the Java SE Platform.
Providers:
The JDK implementation of this module provides an implementation of the jrt file system provider to enumerate and read the class and resource files. See FileSystems.newFileSystem.

summary: Defines the Language Model, Annotation Processing, and Java Compiler APIs.
detail:
Defines the Language Model, Annotation Processing, and Java Compiler APIs.

These APIs model declarations and types of the Java programming language, and define interfaces for tools such as compilers which can be invoked from a program.
